1. *Pazi* da ne spustiš loptu na zemlju! (Watch out not to drop the ball on the ground!)
2. *Pazila* je da ne povredi nečije osećanje. (She was careful not to hurt someone's feelings.)
3. *Pazila* je da ne zakasni na sastanak. (She was careful not to be late for the meeting.)
4. *Pazio* je da ne izgubi priliku. (He was careful not to miss the opportunity.)
5. *Pazili* su da ne pokvare planove. (They were careful not to ruin the plans.)